  "body": "I am specifying my gas limit manually when I send my ethers transaction `300000`.\r\n\r\nThe node will say:\r\n\r\n```\r\neth_sendTransaction\r\n  Contract call:   <UnrecognizedContract>\r\n  Transaction:     0x05f3be84a7517ac591025884f71212afba9458b3e1b2d79d37abf8fdc0fe2580\r\n  From:            0xe92ef3a311a807eaa5a2fbd82aa54ad24c3848d8\r\n  To:              0x2cd0bb9ead1eb1210506aa4cb28c115e201fe65d\r\n  Value:           0 ETH\r\n  Gas used:        291474 of 300000\r\n  Block #10936625: 0x0ae23b8e5a2e5b0206d354a0f1fe5cfba1a88851af285a42354ad264e8fc143e\r\n\r\n  Error: Transaction reverted without a reason`\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut if I increase my gas limit to `400000`:\r\n\r\n```\r\neth_sendTransaction\r\n  Contract call:   <UnrecognizedContract>\r\n  Transaction:     0x958ca422b4cb3eed539981f818d9a75d83e2f9b909ef30bb14c49e2241fdbf49\r\n  From:            0xe92ef3a311a807eaa5a2fbd82aa54ad24c3848d8\r\n  To:              0x2cd0bb9ead1eb1210506aa4cb28c115e201fe65d\r\n  Value:           0 ETH\r\n  Gas used:        155470 of 400000\r\n  Block #10936625: 0x051fa9080c5edd71b681dc057d03163867b2736daa07f32b522329d49c39377a\r\n```\r\n\r\nNote that it actually only needs 155470. Is this expected behaviour?\r\n\r\n\r\nhardhat 2.0.6, forking from mainnet.",
